      "While the European Union has reduced emissions by 32% since 1990 under the European Green Deal, countries like Brazil and India face criticism for failing to meet their climate commitments.",
      "Fossil fuel companies spent $750 million lobbying against climate legislation between 2020 and 2024, despite renewable energy growth, such as solar capacity exceeding 2 terawatts in 2024.",
